Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:16.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others left Dressrosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and are heading for their \Nnext destination, Zou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to meet up with the other half of their crew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, they were attacked by \NBattle Boats out of the blue{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Luffy was taken to an unknown island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:32.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Mine along with Bartolomeo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, you'll join them.\NThis is where your voyage ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the Smelt-Smelt Fruit\Nand became a blast-furnace human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is an ultra-hot blast furnace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smelt ore and produce \Nall kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn you into a nice silver statue\Nbefitting of a man with a bounty of 500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their lives were put in danger by Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.93,0:04:02.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,who is the leader of the \NSilver Pirate Alliance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and while fighting one of his underlings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire, who was also Bartolomeo's \Nchildhood friend,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:12.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they fell into an underground mineshaft\Nwhere they learned the truth about Bill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They defeated Bill's right-hand man, Peseta,\Nwith help from Zoro and the others{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and managed to return above ground\Nonly to confront Bill again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you were the one \Nwho sank our boats that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sank them and saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I perform as good as a stage actor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The simple minded idiot that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,got wrapped up in my dream like a loyal dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take advantage of our compassion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears are pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Desperate Situation!\NLuffy Fights a Battle in Extreme Heat!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic! Oh, so pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, pirates are such hopeless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really believe in immature things\Nlike dreams and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're little better than kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you were very handy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by dangling a dream in front of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you scum became enthralled \Nand worked hard for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing all the treasures\Nand the people with bounties you brought to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be used for me to live\Nthe most luxurious life in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys were working your butts off all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\Nwhat brought you here now, Desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to "settle things."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking you \Ncan defeat me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I'm so underestimated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong? Huh?! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm gonna \Nsmelt you first as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kind of irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait! He's...\N--Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such pure eyes...\NThey make me wanna puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chop you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well done as always!\N--He's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't bring me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how strong a person\Nwith a bounty of 500 million is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Desire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she with Straw Hat and the other one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!\NYou guys were all fooled by Bill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire betrayed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went over to Straw Hat's side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is looking to destroy \Nthe Silver Pirate Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She already took down Avelon and Peseta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:09:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we've been attacked \Nby the Straw Hats because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire masterminded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NGuys, don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw our friends who were abandoned by Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,working as slaves under the ground here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa-whoa! You guys are my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you know I wouldn't \Ndo such a thing to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take down the traitor!\NKill Straw Hat and the other one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How dare he say that without shame...\N--Well, I saw that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're so naive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll break before me like my shield...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! They're just being fooled!\NDon't treat them roughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Smelt-Smelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, let's go back to everyone else.\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's something else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic of you to be defeated\Nby a damn pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the extent of your greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:11:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the Monster of the New World will be\Nquite disappointed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he discards you, that'll be it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.34,0:11:13.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster of the New World...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a king of greed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who once brought my \Npirate crew to our knees
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so easily with the power of money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The face of those giving in to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...discards me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! It's not over for me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you eating too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style 360-Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got to see him but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they wanted to \Nsettle things themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, they'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so easygoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...! It's all melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?\N Is he even human?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was a blast-furnace human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Paramythia-type \NDevil Fruit eater, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's more like Logia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally like an inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done,\Nthe whole island might melt away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to completely smelt everything\Nalong with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retreat for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our retreat is being cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna smelt everyone \Nwho I don't have use for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flowing in from the side too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desire, are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of my hand, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you gonna help Straw \NHat who you respect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become the King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! I'm not gonna let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I become rotten,\NI'm not gonna cast aside a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you {\i1}did{\i0} cast me aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll back you up with all my \Nmight since my support came late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go, Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crest Head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do something about this hot stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle it for you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of it if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier-bility!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:17:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what none of you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A childish thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...survive the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming for the top?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming the King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna shatter your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Grizzly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I fought \Nhand-in-hand with Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My extraordinary dream came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hasn't the situation changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the molten metal that Bill produced\Nis made from real ore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it won't just go away\Neven if you took him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how can we get off of this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry up!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright, don't rush.\N--You're okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let us get on board too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We better leave now!\N--Big Sis and the others aren't here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't wait anymore! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th-That doesn't look good, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have to go help those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vivre Card is moving -\Nthat means he's still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy won't drop dead\Nfrom something of this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The island is sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and our captain \Nare Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm glad they're okay too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were really taken care of by you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:21:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you were.\NDon't ever get fooled by a bad guy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you have nowhere to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:08.39,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE GROUP THAT HELPS LUFFY-{\i1}SENPAI{\i0} TO BECOME\NTHE KING OF THE PIRATES - BARTO CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you join the Barto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out together like we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartolomeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on that one because I'm \Nnot really a fan of Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I've had enough \Nof riding in the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we're gonna rise to the \Ntop of the world of the sea on our own!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our new dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck!\NYou have no chance against Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't know until I try!\NYou'll be sorry for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now, let's go!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright, we gotta get going too!\N--Yes, Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's set sail for Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Grantesoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where the Monster of the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who has power that equals that \Nof the Celestial Dragons, lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ore deposits at Silver Mine \Nsank along with Bill, Tesoro-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already had quite \Na lot of fun with Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real entertainment starts from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dense fog and a turbulent current keep
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:16.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,people away from the legendary island, Zou!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a mysterious 1000-year-old country\Nwhere the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:21.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,native inhabitants, the \NMink Tribe, reign supreme,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:25.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the curtain rises on Luffy's \Nexciting new adventure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Curtain-up on a New Adventure! \NArriving at the Phantom Island, Zou!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.80,0:23:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
